OL,3,CWoman, 96, admits killing pensioner by
OL,4,Cdangerous driving
OL,6,FA 96-year-old woman has pleaded guilty
OL,7,Fto causing death by dangerous driving
OL,8,Fafter her car mounted a pavement and
OL,9,Fhit two pedestrians.
OL,11,FJune Mills, of Ainsdale, Merseyside,
OL,12,Fsat in her wheelchair in the public
OL,13,Fgallery of the courtroom, to enter the
OL,14,Fplea at the Liverpool Crown Court
OL,15,Fhearing on Tuesday.
OL,17,FShe is thought to be the oldest woman
OL,18,Fin Britain to be charged with the
OL,19,Foffence.
