OL,3,CWoman, 96, admits killing pensioner by
OL,4,Cdangerous driving
OL,6,FMills admitted causing the death of
OL,7,FBrenda Joyce, 76, on Elbow Lane in
OL,8,FFormby on 2 August 2023.
OL,10,FAnother pedestrian, an 80-year-old
OL,11,Fwoman, suffered slight injuries.
OL,13,FTom Gent, defending, said Mills was of
OL,14,Fprevious good character and was only
OL,15,Fable to walk a few paces, so would be
OL,16,Funlikely to be fit to carry out unpaid
OL,17,Fwork.
