OL,3,CWoman, 96, admits killing pensioner by
OL,4,Cdangerous driving
OL,6,FHe said her mobility had worsened
OL,7,Fsince the collision, when he said she
OL,8,Fmounted the kerb because she applied
OL,9,Ftoo much accelerator while driving her
OL,10,FVauxhall Corsa.
OL,12,FHe said: "The accelerator pedal fell
OL,13,Fdown beneath her foot, she panicked
OL,14,Fand failed to react to that. She
OL,15,Faccepts by her plea that was driving
OL,16,Fthat was far below standard."
OL,18,FMills is due to be sentenced on 30
OL,19,FSeptember.
